      "range": "2809-2851",
      "markText": "女性主义并非是让女性成为强者的思想，而是一种“寻求让弱者以弱者的姿态得到尊重的思想”",
      "totalCount": 24544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017874&chapterUid=151&rangeStart=2809&rangeEnd=2851",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632250813ab6d7bg014522?chapterUid=151&rangeStart=2809&rangeEnd=2851"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017874_130_3492-3564",
      "chapterUid": 130,
      "range": "3492-3564",
      "markText": "被插入、被得到、成为性的客体，这些说法的另一种表达，就是“被女性化”(feminize)。男人最恐惧的，就是“被女性化”，即性的主体地位的失落。",
      "totalCount": 21913,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017874&chapterUid=130&rangeStart=3492&rangeEnd=3564",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632250813ab6d7bg014522?chapterUid=130&rangeStart=3492&rangeEnd=3564"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017874_129_2480-2544",
      "chapterUid": 129,
      "range": "2480-2544",
      "markText": "每一次想要证明自己是个男人时，都不得不依赖女人这种“恶心污秽不可理喻”的“动物”来满足欲望，男人对这个事实的怨与怒，便是厌女症。",
      "totalCount": 21437,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017874&chapterUid=129&rangeStart=2480&rangeEnd=2544",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632250813ab6d7bg014522?chapterUid=129&rangeStart=2480&rangeEnd=2544"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017874_129_554-625",
      "chapterUid": 129,
      "range": "554-625",
      "markText": "他们只把女人视为泄欲道具，无论哪个女人，只要具有裸体、迷你裙等女性符号，就能让他们发生反应，像巴甫洛夫那条听见铃声便流口水的狗，实在可惊可叹。",
      "totalCount": 17496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017874&chapterUid=129&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=625",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632250813ab6d7bg014522?chapterUid=129&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=625"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017874_129_6582-6660",
      "chapterUid": 129,
      "range": "6582-6660",
      "markText": "如永井这般，在一个阶级和性别严格分界的舞台装置之中，对挣扎在苦海中的女人表达的同情、对她们不幸身世的共情，便成为身处绝对安全圈之内的人们自我满足的精神资源。",
      "totalCount": 16656,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017874&chapterUid=129&rangeStart=6582&rangeEnd=6660",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632250813ab6d7bg014522?chapterUid=129&rangeStart=6582&rangeEnd=6660"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017874_129_1535-1578",
      "chapterUid": 129,
      "range": "1535-1578",
      "markText": "恋物癖并非动物本能，而是高度的文化产物。连巴甫洛夫的狗的反应，也是“学习”规则的结果。",
      "totalCount": 14895,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017874&chapterUid=129&rangeStart=1535&rangeEnd=1578",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632250813ab6d7bg014522?chapterUid=129&rangeStart=1535&rangeEnd=1578"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017874_129_8085-8172",
      "chapterUid": 129,
      "range": "8085-8172",
      "markText": "将女人“他者化”，其实是把女人归入自己能够控制的“他者”范畴之中。这样的他者，既充满魅力又可以轻蔑。无论是将其视为“圣女”来崇拜，还是当作“贱妇”来侮辱，都是一枚硬币的两面。",
      "totalCount": 14722,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017874&chapterUid=129&rangeStart=8085&rangeEnd=8172",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632250813ab6d7bg014522?chapterUid=129&rangeStart=8085&rangeEnd=8172"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017874_129_7141-7220",
      "chapterUid": 129,
      "range": "7141-7220",
      "markText": "与其每次恶心生气，不如换种思维，就像萨义德对东方主义所言，不把男人的作品视为“关于女人的文本”，而是当作“关于男人性幻想的文本”，那么，便会从中学到很多东西。",
      "totalCount": 14346,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017874&chapterUid=129&rangeStart=7141&rangeEnd=7220",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632250813ab6d7bg014522?chapterUid=129&rangeStart=7141&rangeEnd=7220"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017874_129_1907-1980",
      "chapterUid": 129,
      "range": "1907-1980",
      "markText": "好色的厌女症男人都喜欢娼妓。他们的喜欢，并不是把娼妓当作人来爱。他们喜欢的，是对用钱买来的女人的任意玩弄和控制，甚至让她们身不由己地主动服从自己。",
      "totalCount": 14238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017874&chapterUid=129&rangeStart=1907&rangeEnd=1980",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632250813ab6d7bg014522?chapterUid=129&rangeStart=1907&rangeEnd=1980"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017874_131_5525-5586",
